WEBVTT

02:10.080 --> 02:11.320
When the wind blows,

02:11.760 --> 02:13.320
it's time to travel far.

02:14.320 --> 02:15.520
The lighter the leaf,

02:15.880 --> 02:17.480
the farther it will be blown.

02:26.000 --> 02:26.680
Cencen.

02:27.280 --> 02:27.640
Mom.

02:30.000 --> 02:30.530
Let's go.

02:37.680 --> 02:38.240
Sis.

02:39.600 --> 02:40.730
I missed you so much.

02:40.840 --> 02:41.770
Long time no see.

02:43.440 --> 02:45.160
Why do I feel like you've lost weight?

02:45.160 --> 02:46.120
I'm on a diet.

02:46.160 --> 02:47.220
I look good, right?

02:47.320 --> 02:47.920
Honestly.

02:48.000 --> 02:49.200
Say hello to your aunt.

02:49.200 --> 02:49.930
Hello, Aunt.

02:50.640 --> 02:52.640
Xiaocen, you're getting prettier.

02:53.760 --> 02:54.690
Thank you, Aunt.

02:55.079 --> 02:55.800
All right, let's go.

02:55.800 --> 02:56.079
Let's go.

02:56.079 --> 02:57.160
Here, let me help you with your luggage.

02:57.160 --> 02:57.920
No need, Aunt. I got it.

02:57.920 --> 02:58.450
I'm fine.

02:58.600 --> 02:59.680
Let Auntie help you with your luggage.

02:59.680 --> 03:00.210
Let's go.

03:04.000 --> 03:05.000
Come here, Cencen.

03:05.000 --> 03:06.460
Take your medicine first.

03:07.320 --> 03:07.980
Little Sis,

03:08.440 --> 03:11.000
we'll be troubling you for the next few years we're here.

03:11.000 --> 03:12.860
We're family. Don't be so polite.

03:13.240 --> 03:13.880
Actually, Sis,

03:13.880 --> 03:15.240
you didn't have to come all the way here.

03:15.240 --> 03:16.760
With Xiaocen studying in Jingdezhen,

03:16.760 --> 03:18.960
I will definitely take good care of her.

03:20.240 --> 03:22.400
You know Xiaocen's condition.

03:23.320 --> 03:25.160
She's been in poor health since childhood,

03:25.160 --> 03:27.020
and has hardly ever traveled far.

03:27.240 --> 03:29.360
She got into a university in Jingdezhen.

03:29.360 --> 03:30.680
I just came with her.

03:40.240 --> 03:41.370
Sister, are you hot?

03:41.600 --> 03:42.840
Yes. Why is it so hot?

03:42.920 --> 03:44.120
Come in. It's cool inside.

03:44.120 --> 03:44.850
Give it to me.

03:45.160 --> 03:45.820
Let me do it.

03:46.000 --> 03:46.840
Let me do it.

03:49.720 --> 03:50.360
Xing.

03:51.360 --> 03:51.960
Sister,

03:53.440 --> 03:54.370
long time no see.

03:54.480 --> 03:54.880
Sister,

03:54.880 --> 03:56.680
I've already prepared your room.

03:56.680 --> 03:57.360
Xing,

03:57.360 --> 03:58.440
you didn't even greet your Aunt.

03:58.440 --> 03:59.400
How impolite.

04:04.920 --> 04:05.400
No need.

04:05.520 --> 04:06.600
Just stand there.

04:09.680 --> 04:10.600
How are you doing?

04:10.600 --> 04:12.130
Do you feel uncomfortable?

04:12.280 --> 04:12.840
No.

04:13.240 --> 04:14.320
I'm okay.

04:14.760 --> 04:15.880
Give me the pillow.

04:18.480 --> 04:19.079
Alright.

04:20.959 --> 04:22.600
I'll go help your aunt cook.

04:22.600 --> 04:23.600
You tidy up first.

04:23.840 --> 04:24.360
Okay.

04:24.960 --> 04:25.760
Qingying.

04:47.760 --> 04:49.240
Sir, just stop here.

04:50.760 --> 04:51.420
We're here.

04:53.320 --> 04:55.280
It's so nice when there's no traffic.

04:55.280 --> 04:57.210
Come on, Xiaocen. Get out quickly.

04:57.840 --> 04:59.040
Careful getting out.

05:02.360 --> 05:04.520
You have to watch for cars when crossing the street here from now on.

05:04.520 --> 05:06.160
Your school is right across the street.

05:06.160 --> 05:06.760
Thank you.

05:10.000 --> 05:11.040
I have to say,

05:11.040 --> 05:12.360
this school is quite large.

05:12.360 --> 05:12.960
Right?

05:13.040 --> 05:13.880
It's really nice.

05:13.880 --> 05:14.640
I didn't expect this.

05:14.640 --> 05:16.240
There are quite a lot of people.

05:16.240 --> 05:17.240
It's very lively.

05:18.360 --> 05:19.240
There's a river next to it too.

05:19.240 --> 05:19.640
Yeah.

05:19.640 --> 05:20.120
There really is.

05:20.120 --> 05:22.440
There are quite a few clubs at your school.

05:22.440 --> 05:24.100
Yes, look, there are several.

05:24.840 --> 05:26.360
Xiaocen, do you want to take a look?

05:26.360 --> 05:27.240
No need.

05:27.560 --> 05:29.520
Joining clubs is a waste of time.

05:29.680 --> 05:31.120
Focus on your main subjects first.

05:31.120 --> 05:32.080
We can talk about this later.

05:32.080 --> 05:32.610
Let's go.

05:33.120 --> 05:34.040
Come on.

05:39.960 --> 05:40.560
Xiaocen.

05:41.560 --> 05:42.960
There are many snack shops to the north.

05:42.960 --> 05:44.159
I heard they're pretty good.

05:44.159 --> 05:45.920
You can try them when you have time.

05:45.920 --> 05:47.240
What are you talking about?

05:47.240 --> 05:49.080
Snack shop food is the most unhygienic.

05:49.080 --> 05:49.960
Mom, Aunt.

05:50.280 --> 05:51.340
I'll get going now.

05:52.400 --> 05:54.200
Did you forget something again?

05:57.400 --> 05:58.440
Did you set your alarm for your medicine?

05:58.440 --> 05:59.440
I did.

05:59.680 --> 06:00.880
Okay, don't forget.

06:02.040 --> 06:03.400
I'm leaving, Aunt, Mom.

06:03.600 --> 06:04.080
Bye.

06:04.120 --> 06:04.640
Bye.

06:04.920 --> 06:05.450
Go ahead.

06:10.160 --> 06:11.440
How do I wear this?

06:11.600 --> 06:12.730
Just wrap it around.

06:12.760 --> 06:14.000
I received the book from last time.

06:14.000 --> 06:14.930
It's quite good.

06:15.360 --> 06:15.760
Right?

06:16.160 --> 06:16.960
How much is it?

06:17.000 --> 06:17.680
Look.

06:18.280 --> 06:18.720
Here.

06:19.040 --> 06:19.920
I'll scan your code.

06:19.920 --> 06:20.250
Okay.

06:22.960 --> 06:23.560
Hello.

06:24.680 --> 06:25.740
Is this seat taken?

06:26.000 --> 06:27.000
Yes, it is. Sorry.

06:30.640 --> 06:31.560
I'll sit over there.

06:31.560 --> 06:32.320
This is it.

06:35.120 --> 06:36.000
Let me play a round.

06:36.000 --> 06:36.360
Sure.

06:37.840 --> 06:38.560
Yan Xue.

06:39.640 --> 06:41.300
Wait, Yuexin is sitting here.

06:41.760 --> 06:43.090
Then where should I sit?

06:43.120 --> 06:44.080
Anywhere is fine.

06:44.080 --> 06:45.940
Seats haven't been assigned yet.

06:46.320 --> 06:48.080
Hello, can I sit with you?

06:49.440 --> 06:50.159
Sure.

06:55.120 --> 06:55.760
Thank you.

07:01.280 --> 07:03.010
Did you smell something weird?

07:07.760 --> 07:09.120
I don't smell anything.

07:10.080 --> 07:11.080
Am I imagining it?

07:11.440 --> 07:12.280
You choose him.

07:12.280 --> 07:12.920
Right?

07:28.160 --> 07:29.290
This one looks good.

07:53.800 --> 07:54.240
Okay.

07:55.080 --> 07:56.760
Alright, everyone please quiet down.

07:56.760 --> 07:58.159
I am your class teacher.

07:58.280 --> 07:59.240
Now,

07:59.320 --> 08:00.980
let's do something together.

08:08.560 --> 08:09.720
Sitting in a circle

08:09.720 --> 08:10.880
makes it less nerve-wracking, right?

08:10.880 --> 08:12.040
My name is Liang Yiqing.

08:12.040 --> 08:13.520
In the days to come,

08:13.520 --> 08:14.360
I will serve as your

08:14.360 --> 08:14.760
I will serve as your

08:14.760 --> 08:16.120
teacher for Introduction to Cultural Relics,

08:16.120 --> 08:17.360
and your homeroom teacher.

08:17.360 --> 08:18.000
So,

08:18.000 --> 08:19.840
whether in your studies

08:20.000 --> 08:21.080
or in your daily life,

08:21.080 --> 08:23.160
if you have any problems or difficulties,

08:23.160 --> 08:24.360
you can always come to me.

08:24.360 --> 08:24.720
Okay.

08:24.720 --> 08:25.320
All right.

08:25.400 --> 08:27.520
Okay, now that you all know me,

08:27.520 --> 08:29.120
it's my turn to get to know you.

08:29.120 --> 08:30.200
Well then,

08:30.200 --> 08:31.040
let's start with you.

08:31.040 --> 08:31.640
Sure.

08:32.240 --> 08:34.000
Hello everyone, I'm Wang Lin.

08:34.159 --> 08:35.400
I'm from Fuyang, Anhui.

08:35.400 --> 08:36.039
I really like archeology.

08:36.039 --> 08:36.799
We are from the same hometown.

08:36.799 --> 08:38.480
Hello everyone, my name is Li Zhuoting.

08:38.480 --> 08:39.400
My name is Xiaoyi.

08:39.400 --> 08:40.559
I am Wu Jing.

08:41.000 --> 08:41.799
My name is Yan Xue.

08:41.799 --> 08:43.159
I really, really, really

08:43.159 --> 08:44.080
like porcelain.

08:44.080 --> 08:45.960
I usually like watching Korean and Japanese variety shows,

08:45.960 --> 08:47.160
and I also pay a lot of attention to domestic entertainment.

08:47.160 --> 08:48.200
Skateboarding, skiing, and ice skating.

08:48.200 --> 08:49.760
High jump, long jump, and skipping rope.

08:49.760 --> 08:51.520
Just ask me if you need it.

08:51.600 --> 08:53.320
I have dozens of secret

08:53.320 --> 08:54.780
PDFs of celebrity gossip.

08:55.000 --> 08:55.880
If anyone needs it,

08:55.880 --> 08:57.680
feel free to ask me for the cloud drive link.

08:57.680 --> 08:59.560
If you want to play murder mystery games or escape rooms,

08:59.560 --> 09:00.760
remember to hit me up.

09:02.840 --> 09:04.170
My name is Liang Juntao.

09:04.240 --> 09:05.600
And I'm from Jiangxi.

09:07.200 --> 09:09.130
Hello everyone. My name is Xu Xiao.

09:09.760 --> 09:10.890
Nice to meet you all.

09:11.200 --> 09:11.800
Thank you.

09:13.760 --> 09:15.040
Xu Xiao is concise.

09:15.040 --> 09:16.360
Good, very good.

09:16.600 --> 09:17.320
Next student.

09:17.320 --> 09:18.840
Hello, everyone. My name is Zhou Kai.

09:18.840 --> 09:20.320
Hello, everyone. My name is Li Kun.

09:20.320 --> 09:21.380
I'm from Shandong.

09:21.600 --> 09:23.080
People there are honest.

09:23.080 --> 09:24.940
I love eating wheat-based foods.

09:25.080 --> 09:26.120
Right, yes.

09:26.360 --> 09:27.000
Hello, everyone.

09:27.000 --> 09:28.840
My name is Zhao Chen. I'm from Hebei.

09:28.840 --> 09:30.120
So close, so beautiful.

09:30.120 --> 09:31.240
Come to Hebei for the weekend.

09:31.240 --> 09:33.040
Welcome to visit Hebei.

09:33.200 --> 09:33.960
Next student,

09:33.960 --> 09:34.840
please.

09:36.960 --> 09:38.880
Hello everyone, my name is Zhao Xiaocen.

09:38.880 --> 09:40.280
Zhao as in Zhao Yun,

09:40.440 --> 09:42.760
and Cen as in Master Cen.

09:43.720 --> 09:44.800
I wonder if you guys have ever done

09:44.800 --> 09:45.760
an MBTI test.

09:47.400 --> 09:48.720
I am an INFP.

09:48.960 --> 09:50.680
So when you first meet me,

09:50.680 --> 09:52.960
I might seem a bit nervous and quiet.

09:53.200 --> 09:54.000
But deep down,

09:54.000 --> 09:56.160
I really want to be friends with everyone.

09:56.160 --> 09:57.440
I'm a good listener,

09:57.600 --> 09:59.400
so if you have anything on your mind, you can come to me.

09:59.400 --> 10:00.360
I want to be your friend.

10:00.360 --> 10:01.890
Then I'll come to you often.

10:02.400 --> 10:03.680
Good.

10:04.240 --> 10:04.840
Very good.

10:05.960 --> 10:08.020
Great. I just need a friend like this.

10:11.280 --> 10:13.200
Okay. Next student, please.

10:13.880 --> 10:15.680
Hello, everyone. My name is Lin Yuexin.

10:15.680 --> 10:16.880
I don't know if you've ever taken

10:16.880 --> 10:17.800
the MBTI test.

10:18.080 --> 10:20.360
I am a protagonist, ENFJ.

10:20.640 --> 10:21.680
I am extroverted

10:21.680 --> 10:22.840
and I like communicating with everyone.

10:22.840 --> 10:24.840
Someone who likes to help classmates.

10:24.840 --> 10:26.320
If you have any questions,

10:26.400 --> 10:27.560
you can come to me.

10:27.680 --> 10:28.400
I'm the same as you.

10:28.400 --> 10:29.080
Really?

10:29.160 --> 10:29.760
Yes.

10:29.800 --> 10:30.600
Mr. Liang, we are on the same wavelength.

10:30.600 --> 10:32.000
I'm an ENTJ (Commander).

10:32.440 --> 10:33.600
I'm an ENTJ (Commander).

10:33.600 --> 10:33.960
What about you?

10:33.960 --> 10:34.440
Me too.

10:35.400 --> 10:36.480
You too?

10:36.520 --> 10:37.200
We are the same.

10:37.200 --> 10:38.240
Where is it? Let me take a look too.

10:38.240 --> 10:38.800
This one.

10:41.480 --> 10:42.280
Class, class.

10:42.360 --> 10:43.360
This topic,

10:43.400 --> 10:45.040
if we keep talking about it,

10:45.040 --> 10:46.970
we'll probably be here until dark.

10:47.160 --> 10:49.220
All right, let's stop here for today.

10:49.720 --> 10:50.980
Excuse me, classmate.

10:51.240 --> 10:51.900
Classmate.

10:59.160 --> 11:00.160
Hello, everyone.

11:03.640 --> 11:04.400
My name...

11:05.800 --> 11:07.130
My name is Zhao Xiaocen.

11:16.760 --> 11:17.400
Sir.

11:18.800 --> 11:20.960
I don't really know what to say.

11:21.800 --> 11:23.520
Xiaocen might be a little nervous.

11:23.520 --> 11:25.450
Let's give her a round of applause.

11:31.200 --> 11:31.520
I...

11:31.840 --> 11:32.320
I...

11:37.400 --> 11:38.530
It's okay, Xiaocen.

11:39.000 --> 11:40.560
You're probably just too nervous today.

11:40.560 --> 11:41.720
We can get to know each other later.

11:41.720 --> 11:42.780
Please take a seat.

11:48.280 --> 11:49.340
It's finally over.

11:51.360 --> 11:52.620
Don't forget tonight.

11:52.800 --> 11:53.760
The whole class is going.

11:53.760 --> 11:54.160
Okay.

11:54.560 --> 11:55.200
Okay, bye.

11:55.600 --> 11:56.040
Bye.

11:57.520 --> 11:58.050
Xiaocen.

11:58.360 --> 11:59.360
What do you want to eat?

11:59.360 --> 11:59.960
Yuexin.

12:00.800 --> 12:02.730
Are you going to the party tonight?

12:04.480 --> 12:05.240
A gathering?

12:05.840 --> 12:06.280
Yes.

12:06.560 --> 12:07.320
A notice was sent in the group.

12:07.320 --> 12:08.580
Didn't you receive it?

12:09.080 --> 12:10.000
What group?

12:10.440 --> 12:11.640
You were absent during military training.

12:11.640 --> 12:13.040
We created a class group back then.

12:13.040 --> 12:14.280
I'll invite you in a bit.

12:14.280 --> 12:14.800
Okay.

12:16.600 --> 12:17.080
But

12:17.680 --> 12:20.340
I promised my mom I'd go home for dinner tonight.

12:20.480 --> 12:23.040
Then just tell your mom you're not going back tonight.

12:23.040 --> 12:23.480
Yeah.

12:23.960 --> 12:25.040
We're all going.

12:25.280 --> 12:27.000
And it's our first time having dinner together.

12:27.000 --> 12:28.000
Just come with us.

12:31.240 --> 12:32.000
Okay.

12:36.440 --> 12:37.040
This is it.

12:37.560 --> 12:38.480
Looks pretty good.

12:38.480 --> 12:39.360
Smells so nice.

12:39.360 --> 12:39.960
Not bad.

12:40.680 --> 12:41.210
Let's go.

12:41.360 --> 12:42.890
Yan Xue, what are you doing?

12:43.080 --> 12:43.880
Over here.

12:44.320 --> 12:45.000
I got four dips.

12:45.000 --> 12:45.960
Which one do you guys want?

12:45.960 --> 12:46.720
Let me help you with that.

12:46.720 --> 12:47.650
I'll go in first.

12:47.880 --> 12:49.320
Okay, this is yours.

12:50.600 --> 12:52.560
Here, let me hand out the chopsticks.

12:52.560 --> 12:53.220
Here you go.

12:53.960 --> 12:54.960
Here, hold this.

12:55.360 --> 12:56.680
I really like that show.

12:56.680 --> 12:57.280
It's also about cultural relics.

12:57.280 --> 12:58.480
I want some, give me a pair.

12:58.480 --> 12:59.480
Your chopsticks.

12:59.840 --> 13:01.440
Give me a pair of chopsticks.

13:02.040 --> 13:03.040
Yan Xue, hurry up.

13:03.200 --> 13:04.200
The food is almost ready.

13:04.200 --> 13:04.800
Hold on a second.

13:04.800 --> 13:05.720
Yan Xue, stop working.

13:05.720 --> 13:06.520
I want some.

13:06.880 --> 13:07.200
Here.

13:07.200 --> 13:07.760
Thanks.

13:08.200 --> 13:09.720
Who doesn't have chopsticks yet?

13:09.720 --> 13:10.160
Here, give it to me.

13:10.160 --> 13:11.240
Give me another pair of chopsticks.

13:11.240 --> 13:12.370
Is it not cooked yet?

13:12.560 --> 13:13.960
No, it's not ready yet.

13:13.960 --> 13:16.640
Wait until it's cooked before you add vegetables.

13:16.640 --> 13:17.640
Should we eat the vegetables now?

13:17.640 --> 13:18.360
I'll put it in for you.

13:18.360 --> 13:18.960
Thank you.

13:19.880 --> 13:21.040
Finally free.

13:21.320 --> 13:22.680
Military training was miserable.

13:22.680 --> 13:25.280
Waking up at five every day to fold those blankets.

13:25.280 --> 13:26.960
They have to be folded into perfectly square

13:26.960 --> 13:28.040
tofu blocks.

13:28.800 --> 13:30.080
It's too hard.

13:30.120 --> 13:31.520
Really, I didn't fold mine at all.

13:31.520 --> 13:32.560
There's one more thing.

13:32.560 --> 13:34.820
I'm not used to showering with everyone.

13:34.960 --> 13:36.560
You all got tortured by military training,

13:36.560 --> 13:37.080
while I

13:37.280 --> 13:38.520
got tortured by Li Zhuoting.

13:38.520 --> 13:38.880
Stop talking.

13:38.880 --> 13:40.160
What happened to you two?

13:40.160 --> 13:41.440
What's going on with you guys?

13:41.440 --> 13:43.600
Every time the instructor brought the food out,

13:43.600 --> 13:44.640
as long as he was there,

13:44.640 --> 13:45.800
I couldn't get any meat.

13:45.800 --> 13:46.480
Come on, eat.

13:46.480 --> 13:47.320
Stop talking, just eat.

13:47.320 --> 13:48.640
He steals food so fast.

13:48.960 --> 13:49.760
As soon as he pounces on it,

13:49.760 --> 13:50.800
if you look in the pot,

13:50.800 --> 13:51.800
there's only soup left.

13:51.800 --> 13:52.760
Stop talking nonsense, okay?

13:52.760 --> 13:53.600
I'm not that dramatic.

13:53.600 --> 13:54.640
It is that dramatic.

13:54.640 --> 13:55.770
By the way, Xiaocen,

13:56.080 --> 13:58.610
why didn't you join us for military training?

13:58.840 --> 14:00.640
My mom got me a sick leave.

14:00.880 --> 14:01.400
Sick leave?

14:01.400 --> 14:02.660
What's wrong with you?

14:03.600 --> 14:04.840
It's nothing serious.

14:04.840 --> 14:07.400
I just had a weak constitution as a kid,

14:07.400 --> 14:09.000
and I get heatstroke easily.

14:09.400 --> 14:11.000
You can avoid military training with heatstroke?

14:11.000 --> 14:12.530
Then I have heatstroke too.

14:13.520 --> 14:14.600
Eat more.

14:14.640 --> 14:15.720
Okay, come on.

14:16.080 --> 14:18.440
Let's toast with soft drinks instead of alcohol.

14:18.440 --> 14:18.960
Let's make a toast.

14:18.960 --> 14:19.420
Come on.

14:19.800 --> 14:20.880
Come on, cheers.

14:21.160 --> 14:23.120
We've survived the hard days of military training.

14:23.120 --> 14:25.080
Here's to our college years.

14:25.080 --> 14:27.400
May everything go smoothly and happily.

14:27.400 --> 14:30.080
And most importantly, may we love each other.

14:30.080 --> 14:30.440
Definitely.

14:30.440 --> 14:30.720
Okay.

14:30.720 --> 14:31.280
Cheers.

14:31.320 --> 14:31.640
Come on.

14:31.640 --> 14:32.360
Cheers, cheers.

14:32.360 --> 14:32.960
Cheers, cheers.

14:32.960 --> 14:33.420
Come on.

14:33.480 --> 14:33.960
Come on.

14:36.360 --> 14:37.760
Cheers, cheers, cheers.

14:39.040 --> 14:39.840
That feels great.

14:39.840 --> 14:41.240
Move your stool forward.

14:41.600 --> 14:42.400
All right, come on.

14:42.400 --> 14:43.680
Let's talk about something else.

14:43.680 --> 14:44.640
Do you remember

14:45.080 --> 14:46.880
those late-night marches?

14:47.080 --> 14:48.080
At 1 a.m.

14:49.000 --> 14:49.600
I remember.

14:49.600 --> 14:50.360
Emergency assembly.

14:50.360 --> 14:51.320
I was exhausted.

14:51.400 --> 14:52.680
Why are you so excited?

15:02.200 --> 15:04.400
Cheers.

15:06.560 --> 15:08.080
Is the pork fat?

15:08.160 --> 15:09.680
Fat.

15:09.680 --> 15:10.400
Okay.

15:11.160 --> 15:12.420
I've booked a KTV room.

15:12.520 --> 15:14.200
Watch me show off my singing tonight.

15:14.200 --> 15:15.160
Let's go.

15:15.160 --> 15:17.360
I'm telling you, I'll definitely sing 10 songs.

15:17.360 --> 15:17.840
Yuexin.

15:19.560 --> 15:20.360
What's wrong?

15:20.560 --> 15:21.840
Tonight,

15:21.920 --> 15:23.980
my mom is still waiting for me at home.

15:24.360 --> 15:25.120
So...

15:26.360 --> 15:28.220
Can't your mom make an exception?

15:31.080 --> 15:32.080
If it really doesn't work out,

15:32.080 --> 15:33.940
we'll just have to do it next time.

15:34.560 --> 15:36.020
Yuexin, Yan Xue, let's go.

15:36.680 --> 15:37.560
Okay, coming.

15:37.760 --> 15:38.080
I'm leaving.

15:38.080 --> 15:39.080
I'm leaving. Bye.

15:39.760 --> 15:40.120
Bye.

15:40.120 --> 15:40.850
I'm leaving.

15:43.480 --> 15:44.360
Coming.

15:44.360 --> 15:45.640
What song did you sing?

15:46.040 --> 15:46.640
Let's go.

15:46.640 --> 15:47.640
It's so slippery.

15:47.720 --> 15:48.250
Hurry up.

15:59.080 --> 16:01.360
It shows the night market is right around here.

16:01.360 --> 16:03.560
Really? Check if you got the direction wrong.

16:03.560 --> 16:04.400
Hello, sir.

16:06.480 --> 16:09.010
I am heading towards the pinned location now.

16:38.240 --> 16:39.000
Hello, sir.

16:40.440 --> 16:42.080
I'm on this street right now.

16:43.400 --> 16:44.480
I don't see you.

16:47.280 --> 16:48.080
All right.

16:48.120 --> 16:49.380
I'll call another cab.

16:50.840 --> 16:51.960
Okay. Thank you.

17:02.240 --> 17:03.840
Take a look at the porcelain.

17:03.880 --> 17:05.740
Big ones for 15, small ones for 20.

17:07.560 --> 17:09.020
Can you give me a discount?

17:10.079 --> 17:10.880
Young man.

17:11.400 --> 17:13.359
Look at the craftsmanship of this small one.

17:13.359 --> 17:14.619
Look at the outlining.

17:16.520 --> 17:17.960
Sir, you're so nice.

17:22.839 --> 17:24.440
Blue-and-white porcelain.

17:25.119 --> 17:27.650
Take a look at the blue-and-white porcelain.

17:31.320 --> 17:32.240
Cup sets.

17:35.080 --> 17:35.720
Cloud cup.

17:38.680 --> 17:40.360
Sir, the price I just mentioned,

17:40.360 --> 17:41.690
can you sell it for that?

17:42.080 --> 17:43.680
Go ask around on this street.

18:11.600 --> 18:13.560
You are Xu Xiao, right?

18:14.080 --> 18:15.040
Hi, I am...

18:15.040 --> 18:15.900
I remember you.

18:17.360 --> 18:19.560
During the class self-introductions,

18:19.600 --> 18:22.060
we were the only ones who just gave our names.

18:26.400 --> 18:27.920
Where... where is this place?

18:27.920 --> 18:29.520
Why are there so many stalls?

18:29.880 --> 18:31.010
This is Taoxichuan.

18:31.120 --> 18:34.240
It's the largest cultural and creative market in Jingdezhen.

18:34.240 --> 18:34.680
Sir.

18:35.560 --> 18:36.760
Xu Xiao, you're here.

18:37.600 --> 18:39.460
Here's what you were looking for.

18:39.600 --> 18:40.200
Thank you.

18:40.960 --> 18:41.820
All good stuff.

18:43.960 --> 18:44.420
Thanks.

18:44.840 --> 18:45.770
You're welcome.

18:46.880 --> 18:47.410
How much?

18:47.600 --> 18:48.460
Same as before.

18:48.800 --> 18:49.130
Okay.

18:50.680 --> 18:52.940
You have to pay for these broken ones too?

18:53.960 --> 18:56.480
They are broken porcelain pieces from the Ming and Qing Dynasties.

18:56.480 --> 18:58.120
Then they are antiques.

18:59.000 --> 19:00.060
Ancient porcelain

19:00.200 --> 19:01.920
is also divided into folk kilns and imperial kilns.

19:01.920 --> 19:03.720
These are broken pieces from folk kilns,

19:03.720 --> 19:05.650
so the price is not very expensive.

19:06.000 --> 19:06.920
Folk kilns.

19:07.240 --> 19:07.770
Let's go.

19:08.400 --> 19:10.800
Folk kilns and imperial kilns.

19:21.720 --> 19:23.440
Miss, look at these porcelain decals.

19:23.440 --> 19:24.370
They're pretty.

19:24.840 --> 19:25.400
Well,

19:26.120 --> 19:27.250
they are closing up.

19:27.400 --> 19:28.600
I'll head back first.

19:28.800 --> 19:29.800
See you at school.

19:32.360 --> 19:33.280
Whatever you think is fair.

19:33.280 --> 19:33.840
Buy a few.

19:35.000 --> 19:36.280
Just don't give too little.

19:36.280 --> 19:36.920
Okay, okay.

19:36.920 --> 19:38.320
I'll take these two then.

19:39.520 --> 19:40.320
Come again, beautiful.

19:40.320 --> 19:41.320
Okay, okay.

19:47.160 --> 19:48.160
Let's walk ahead.

19:49.280 --> 19:50.210
How about there?

20:08.440 --> 20:11.100
It's hard to get a cab here when the stalls close.

20:11.640 --> 20:12.640
Where do you live?

20:14.640 --> 20:15.640
Yuyao Jingxiang.

20:16.800 --> 20:18.330
You can just take bus No. 13.

20:18.520 --> 20:19.120
Follow me.

21:54.960 --> 21:55.520
I'm here.

22:04.880 --> 22:05.280
Wait.

22:08.400 --> 22:10.200
I'm getting off at this stop too.

22:10.720 --> 22:11.250
Let's go.

22:36.840 --> 22:38.440
Why didn't you go

22:38.440 --> 22:39.970
to the class reunion today?

22:41.560 --> 22:42.960
I have my own things to do.

22:43.240 --> 22:43.960
Besides,

22:44.800 --> 22:45.920
we are not so close

22:46.120 --> 22:47.720
that we have to eat together.

22:48.360 --> 22:49.960
Aren't you worried

22:50.080 --> 22:52.140
that you won't get along with others,

22:53.520 --> 22:55.250
or being isolated by everyone?

22:56.400 --> 22:57.080
Not at all.

22:58.440 --> 22:59.700
If anyone isolates me,

23:00.320 --> 23:01.380
I'll isolate them.

23:15.280 --> 23:15.800
Well...

23:17.400 --> 23:18.000
I'm here.

23:18.640 --> 23:18.970
Okay.

23:20.400 --> 23:22.000
I still have a few more stops.

23:25.080 --> 23:26.140
I'll get off first.

23:28.680 --> 23:29.160
Bye.

23:30.840 --> 23:31.280
Bye.

24:35.520 --> 24:38.400
Why did I ride past my stop with her?

24:45.840 --> 24:46.400
And these.

24:46.400 --> 24:47.400
I thought we only needed clay.

24:47.400 --> 24:48.760
The tools are so complete.

24:48.760 --> 24:49.820
So well-equipped.

24:50.920 --> 24:52.000
This is so much fun. Look at this.

24:52.000 --> 24:53.480
Hurry up and wash your hands. Come on.

24:53.480 --> 24:54.920
I think that one looks like...

24:54.920 --> 24:56.040
There's so much paint.

24:56.040 --> 24:57.100
Don't move around.

24:57.440 --> 24:58.760
Be careful, be careful.

24:58.760 --> 24:59.690
Wash your hands.

25:00.720 --> 25:02.980
I can't believe there's a name like this.

25:05.520 --> 25:07.580
Why are you two standing so straight?

25:07.960 --> 25:11.000
I heard the teachers in our major are very strict.

25:11.200 --> 25:11.680
Yes.

25:12.160 --> 25:14.400
He often scolds the students so much that they dare not enter the classroom.

25:14.400 --> 25:15.080
So strict?

25:15.520 --> 25:16.320
Here he comes.

25:21.160 --> 25:23.600
Welcome to the cultural relics restoration class.

25:23.600 --> 25:25.800
My name is Yue Qixin.

25:28.000 --> 25:29.360
Cultural relics restoration

25:29.360 --> 25:30.640
is a technique.

25:32.360 --> 25:32.960
Of course.

25:33.480 --> 25:36.800
Some students already have a certain foundation.

25:36.840 --> 25:37.720
But I believe

25:38.120 --> 25:39.320
through this course,

25:39.680 --> 25:42.120
you should achieve one, two,

25:42.280 --> 25:43.960
or even more breakthroughs.

25:44.280 --> 25:46.840
To have a newer

25:47.000 --> 25:48.920
and more proper understanding of cultural relics restoration.

25:48.920 --> 25:50.160
Come, bring the plates over.

25:50.160 --> 25:51.160
Help yourselves.

25:51.280 --> 25:51.760
Go.

26:07.840 --> 26:09.520
Students who didn't get a plate,

26:09.520 --> 26:11.000
pair up with those who did.

26:11.040 --> 26:13.080
Form groups of two freely.

26:13.160 --> 26:14.280
I don't have a plate.

26:14.280 --> 26:15.440
Wang Lin, let's team up.

26:15.440 --> 26:16.240
Absolutely.

26:16.760 --> 26:17.090
Okay.

26:17.280 --> 26:18.410
Then let's be a team.

26:18.720 --> 26:20.120
What do we do now?

26:20.120 --> 26:21.120
I have no idea.

26:22.240 --> 26:23.700
What are we supposed to do?

26:24.560 --> 26:25.280
We are a team.

26:25.280 --> 26:25.720
Okay.

26:26.520 --> 26:27.240
This looks really nice.

26:27.240 --> 26:28.080
I don't really like this pattern.

26:28.080 --> 26:28.740
Me neither.

26:28.920 --> 26:30.360
This is so beautiful.

26:31.080 --> 26:32.280
I'll team up with you.

26:34.000 --> 26:34.720
Is that okay?
